ActDepartment of Veterans Affairs Act
SubjectOrder Assigning to the Minister of Veterans Affairs to develop, establish and implement the Veteran and Family Telemedicine Services (VFTS) Pilot
PrecisOrder Assigning to the Minister of Veterans Affairs to develop, establish and implement the VETERAN AND FAMILY TELEMEDICINE SERVICES (VTFS) PILOT in order to provide eligible CAF Veterans and their families with access to up to two years of virtual care service while they transition to the provincial/territorial insured health care system.
